00:56:08,000 --> 00:56:13,438
'Dear diary, my teen angst bullshit
has a body count.

764
00:56:13,520 --> 00:56:16,671
'The most popular people
in school are dead.

765
00:56:16,760 --> 00:56:21,356
'Everybody's sad
but it's a weird kind of sad.

766
00:56:21,440 --> 00:56:26,594
'Suicide gave Heather depth,
Kurt a soul, Ram a brain.

767
00:56:27,720 --> 00:56:29,676
'I don't know what it's given me

768
00:56:29,760 --> 00:56:34,311
'but I've got no control
over myself when I'm with JD.

769
00:56:34,400 --> 00:56:37,278
