through togetherness.

788
00:57:45,240 --> 00:57:48,596
I want everyone to clasp hands.

789
00:57:48,680 --> 00:57:52,389
We need to connect this cafeteria
into one mighty circuit!

790
00:57:52,480 --> 00:57:55,392
- Excuse me.
- Here comes the TV crew!

791
00:57:55,480 --> 00:57:57,232
Lock your paws!

792
00:57:57,320 --> 00:57:59,959
- We're ready when you are.
- Hi, there.

793
00:58:01,000 --> 00:58:04,993
Come on. Let's go. Here.

794
00:58:05,080 --> 00:58:07,913
This will be on TV.
Let's show them how you feel!

795
00:58:08,000 --> 00:58:11,390
