801
00:58:28,000 --> 00:58:30,639
Those fish sticks can wait. Let's go.

802
00:58:30,720 --> 00:58:32,676
Come on, kids!

803
00:58:34,520 --> 00:58:36,795
The whole world is watching!

804
00:58:39,120 --> 00:58:41,315
Show them that you care!

805
00:58:42,400 --> 00:58:45,039
Greetings and salutations.

806
00:58:45,120 --> 00:58:49,875
I'll need a VHS copy of this by Monday
