don't let suicide get you down.

808
00:58:56,200 --> 00:58:58,668
That thing this afternoon,

809
00:58:58,760 --> 00:59:01,513
I'm so angry, it was chaos, fucking chaos.

810
00:59:02,960 --> 00:59:04,837
What are you talking about?

811
00:59:04,920 --> 00:59:08,629
I mean, today was great.
Chaos was great.

812
00:59:08,720 --> 00:59:12,030
Chaos is what killed the dinosaurs, darling.

813
00:59:13,320 --> 00:59:15,436
Face it, our way is the way.

814
00:59:15,520 --> 00:59:17,954
We scare people into not being assholes.

