00:59:18,040 --> 00:59:20,634
Our way is not our way.

816
00:59:20,720 --> 00:59:23,553
Oh, yeah? Tell that to the judge, all right?

817
00:59:23,640 --> 00:59:25,471
Tell it to Kurt Kelly.

818
00:59:25,560 --> 00:59:27,915
I'm telling it to you.

819
00:59:30,280 --> 00:59:32,350
God, you can be so immature.

820
00:59:32,440 --> 00:59:36,035
