821
00:59:37,680 --> 00:59:39,750
We beat the bitches.

822
00:59:39,840 --> 00:59:42,308
Beautiful. The beaver's home.

823
00:59:42,400 --> 00:59:45,358
Judge told them to slurp shit and die.

824
00:59:45,440 --> 00:59:48,955
I put a Norwegian in the boiler room.

825
00:59:49,040 --> 00:59:51,429
Masterful.

826
