it set off a pack of thermals I stuck upstairs.

828
01:00:07,280 --> 01:00:09,589
Some days it's great to be alive.

829
01:00:12,040 --> 01:00:14,429
Stick it to those goddamn...

830
01:00:14,520 --> 01:00:16,476
Do you like your father?

831
01:00:17,920 --> 01:00:20,354
Never given the matter much thought.

832
01:00:23,240 --> 01:00:25,196
Liked my mother.

833
01:00:26,000 --> 01:00:29,072
They said her death was an accident

834
01:00:29,160 --> 01:00:31,993
but she knew what she was doing.

835
01:00:32,080 --> 01:00:36,949
She walked into the building two minutes
before my dad blew the place up.

836
01:00:37,040 --> 01:00:40,191
She waved at me and then...

837
01:00:40,280 --> 01:00:42,236
boom.

838
01:00:42,320 --> 01:00:46,108
'Dudes, if I get one more request
for that Big Fun song,

839
01:00:46,200 --> 01:00:47,918
'I'm gonna commit suicide.'

840
01:00:48,000 --> 01:00:49,752
Playing our song.

841
01:00:49,840 --> 01:00:52,479
'Here it is, Teenage Suicide Don't Do It.'

842
01:00:53,960 --> 01:00:57,236
# Teenage suicide
# Don't do it

843
01:00:57,320 --> 01:00:59,788
# Teenage suicide
# She blew it

844
01:00:59,880 --> 01:01:01,950
# Teenage suicide

845
01:01:02,040 --> 01:01:03,314
# Don't do it... #

846
01:01:05,880 --> 01:01:07,916
That's it. We're breaking up.

847
01:01:08,000 --> 01:01:11,310
What? You can't bring them back,
you must know that.

848
01:01:11,400 --> 01:01:15,439
I'm not trying to bring anybody back
except maybe myself.

849
01:01:26,080 --> 01:01:27,911
No!

850
01:01:29,400 --> 01:01:32,198
To think once
I actually thought you were cool.

851
01:01:32,280 --> 01:01:36,717
If you can't deal with me now
then just stay home and shoot your TV,

852
01:01:36,800 --> 01:01:39,394
blow up a couple toasters or something.

853
01:01:39,480 --> 01:01:43,553
