Me and Martha Dumptruck?

856
01:02:02,120 --> 01:02:03,917
Where did you get this?

857
01:02:05,080 --> 01:02:09,437
Oh, I just had the nicest little chat
with Ms Dumptruck.

858
01:02:09,520 --> 01:02:11,556
Got along famously.

859
01:02:11,640 --> 01:02:14,996
It's scary how everybody's got
a little story to tell.

860
01:02:15,080 --> 01:02:17,514
Want to see the canoeing shots?

861
01:02:17,600 --> 01:02:19,431
What is this? Blackmail?

862
01:02:23,520 --> 01:02:25,670
I'll give you a week's lunch money.

863
01:02:27,840 --> 01:02:31,549
I don't want your money.
I want your strength.

864
01:02:31,640 --> 01:02:34,677
Westerburg does not need
mushy togetherness,

865
01:02:34,760 --> 01:02:36,955
it needs a strong leader.

866
01:02:37,040 --> 01:02:40,077
Heather Chandler was that leader but...

867
01:02:40,160 --> 01:02:42,549
But she couldn't handle it.

868
01:02:42,640 --> 01:02:44,631
I think you can.

869
01:02:45,720 --> 01:02:47,676
Moby Dick is dunked.

870
01:02:47,760 --> 01:02:52,436
The white whale drank some bad plankton
and splashed through a coffee table

871
01:02:52,520 --> 01:02:55,159
