978
01:10:59,520 --> 01:11:01,511
'like some mythological thing

979
01:11:01,600 --> 01:11:04,990
'my eighth-grade boyfriend
would have known about.

980
01:11:06,160 --> 01:11:08,958
'Heather's even doing the old note trick.

981
01:11:11,080 --> 01:11:13,799
' I've seen JD's way.

982
01:11:13,880 --> 01:11:17,555
'I've seen Miss Pauline Fleming's way

983
01:11:17,640 --> 01:11:19,596
'and nothing has changed.

984
01:11:19,680 --> 01:11:21,910
'I guess that's Heather's way.

985
01:11:22,000 --> 01:11:24,719
'And, Jesus, what about JD?

986
01:11:24,800 --> 01:11:27,189
'I can't get him out of my head.

987
01:11:27,280 --> 01:11:29,714
'Wait. Where's Heather going? '

988
01:11:29,800 --> 01:11:31,950
Where's Heather going?

989
01:11:32,040 --> 01:11:34,190
She's going to cry.

990
